Order 5V power supply and use shift registers for led strip clock (not max72xx), as here:
    http://videooko.net/?p=895
    http://videooko.net/?p=854

see adc.w to control brightness
https://arduino.stackexchange.com/questions/58240/vary-voltage-using-relay-is-this-possible


After you connect 7-segment MAX7219, rm "echo minute-second ..." from tel.w and rebuild and reflash raspberry (build-clock.sh) and rm "case '0'" from "Main menu" in tel.w
